00:16:41.840 --> 00:16:42.440
What is it?

00:16:42.440 --> 00:16:43.930
AUDIENCE: Males and females?

00:16:43.930 --> 00:16:45.370
PROFESSOR: People.

00:16:45.370 --> 00:16:47.670
Yeah, so we're going
to have people.

