In fact, there's two
kinds of people here.

00:16:50.290 --> 00:16:52.630
There's men, and women.

00:16:55.370 --> 00:17:01.520
All right we got nodes
here for the men.

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:05.400
And in fact in America,
