get different colors.

00:32:03.154 --> 00:32:08.120
All right, and then the minimum
number of colors you need

00:32:08.120 --> 00:32:11.750
is called the chromatic
number of the graph.

00:32:11.750 --> 00:32:36.460
So the minimum value of K, for
which such a coloring exist,

00:32:36.460 --> 00:32:48.840
is the chromatic
number OF the graph.

00:32:48.840 --> 00:32:59.956
And it's denoted by
this symbol chi of G.

